{"tid":1056320,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗與7有緣　任中國柒牌時裝代言人","createTime":"2019-03-11T06:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T06:42:06.000Z","uid":56533,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e37741446b60d2e53bfa6265220b9937a5ab0aa","tid":1056320,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190311/large/1552270774_3d26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190311%2Flarge%2F1552270774_3d26.jpg&h=3ea1f8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國柒牌時裝在官方微博宣佈，將會由祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度（C朗）出任全新代言人，不論在球會或葡萄牙國家隊都是穿7號球衣的C朗可謂與「柒」有緣。<br />\n<br />\n柒牌官方微博日前發帖，讓人猜將於3月10揭曉的商務男裝代言人是誰，猜中者更有機會獲得神秘禮物。當時該帖上載的是一張看不清樣子的背光照，讓人猜「誰是傳奇」，謎面如下︰<br />\n「TA，以獨創設計揚名天下<br />\n他，以超凡實力稱霸C位<br />\nTA，持續創新，引領中國男士時尚風潮<br />\n他，追求極致，以29個冠軍笑傲群雄<br />\nTA，是中國男裝領軍品牌，柒牌；那他，究竟是誰？！<br />\n2019.3.10 重磅揭曉！<br />\n轉發大聲說出你的猜想，3月9日20點前猜中的幸運兒，有機會獲得神秘禮物 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190311/large/1552271628_afcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190311%2Flarge%2F1552271628_afcf.jpg&h=23037769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果，柒牌的最新代言人原來是C朗，而他的前輩、同為葡萄牙國家隊7號的費高，早於2004年已曾經擔任柒牌代言人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190311/59354951?fbclid=IwAR3Ej0MiRE1cCrf7YgG86HL3qojpj_nKNBhNCsHEJr6vMhoDkTszjuhN0PA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59354951%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ej0MiRE1cCrf7YgG86HL3qojpj_nKNBhNCsHEJr6vMhoDkTszjuhN0PA&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=ad9e90de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190311%2F59354951%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Ej0MiRE1cCrf7YgG86HL3qojpj_nKNBhNCsHEJr6vMhoDkTszjuhN0PA&h=9941ded4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190311/59354951?fbclid=IwAR3Ej0MiRE1cCrf7YgG86HL3qojpj_nKNBhNCsHEJr6vMhoDkTszjuhN0PA</a>"},{"pid":"823c7e6b2d83382a47a1b64a4505d87832db278a","tid":1056320,"uid":82851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"張宣傳照英文咁大 中文咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國仲唔輸番次"},{"pid":"b21b798c82939f75a26163ec925eee8cb711641d","tid":1056320,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2hoak.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2hoak.gif&h=f668c696&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}